Directories explained:
cwl-version: when lightning scripts become cwl, they go here
doc: documentation
go: originally Lightning was to be written in go, but now is written
in c++. Many go scripts are still used and live here.
img: when documentation contains images, they end up here.
prototype: vestigial directory
proxy: vestigial directory
sandbox: testing, playing, experimenting
tools: main directory, where usefule scripts live

